<center><h1>About Us</h1></center>

<center>
    <img src="~/images/logo/fgsfhsdfdf.jpg" height="100px" style="align-content:center" />
</center>
<p>Welcome to Zoro Cycle Shop! We are delighted to share our story with you. Our shop is dedicated to providing the best cycling products and services to our valued customers. Here, you'll learn about our history, mission, product range, services, community involvement, customer testimonials, and future goals. We hope this gives you a comprehensive understanding of who we are and what we stand for.</p>

<center>
    <h2>Our History</h2>
</center>
<center>
    <img src="~/images/logo/our history logo.jpeg" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" />
</center>
<p>Zoro Cycle Shop was founded in 2005 by avid cyclist and entrepreneur, John Doe. John’s vision was to create a space where cyclists of all levels could find quality bikes and accessories while receiving top-notch customer service. Over the years, our shop has grown from a small local store to a well-respected name in the cycling community. We have expanded our product range, added new services, and built a loyal customer base. Our journey has been fueled by a passion for cycling and a commitment to excellence.</p>


<center>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
</center>

<center><img src="~/images/logo/mission-logo-9.jpg" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" /></center>
<p>Our mission is simple: to help you find the perfect bike and accessories to enjoy your ride. Whether you're a seasoned cyclist or just starting out, we believe that everyone should have access to the best cycling products and services. We strive to provide a welcoming environment where you can explore, learn, and find everything you need for your cycling adventures.</p>

<center>
    <h2>Our Product Range</h2>
    </center>

<center>
    <img src="~/images/logo/range.png" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" />
    </center>
<p>At Zoro Cycle Shop, we offer a wide range of bicycles to suit every rider's needs. Our selection includes:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Road Bikes:</strong> Perfect for those who love speed and long-distance rides on paved surfaces. Our road bikes are lightweight, aerodynamic, and built for performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Mountain Bikes:</strong> Designed for off-road adventures, our mountain bikes are rugged, durable, and capable of handling rough terrain.</li>
    <li><strong>Hybrid Bikes:</strong> Combining features of road and mountain bikes, our hybrid bikes are versatile and ideal for various riding conditions.</li>
    <li><strong>Electric Bikes:</strong> Offering an extra boost, our electric bikes make commuting and long rides more accessible and enjoyable.</li>
    <li><strong>Kids' Bikes:</strong> Safe and fun, our kids' bikes come in various sizes and styles to get young riders started on their cycling journey.</li>
</ul>
<p>In addition to bikes, we carry a wide range of accessories, including helmets, lights, locks, clothing, and maintenance tools. Our products are sourced from reputable brands known for their quality and reliability.</p>

<center>
    <h2>Our Services</h2></center>
<center>
    <img src="~/images/logo/plumbing-clipart-hvac-18.png" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" />
    </center>
<p>We believe that excellent products should be complemented by excellent services. At Zoro Cycle Shop, we offer a variety of services to meet your cycling needs:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Bike Fitting:</strong> Proper bike fit is crucial for comfort and performance. Our experts use advanced tools to ensure your bike is tailored to your body and riding style.</li>
    <li><strong>Repairs and Maintenance:</strong> Our experienced technicians provide comprehensive repair and maintenance services. From fixing a flat tire to a full bike overhaul, we've got you covered.</li>
    <li><strong>Custom Builds:</strong> If you have a specific vision for your bike, we can help make it a reality. We offer custom bike builds to match your preferences and requirements.</li>
    <li><strong>Bike Rentals:</strong> Visiting from out of town or want to try a different type of bike? Our rental service offers a range of bikes for short-term use.</li>
    <li><strong>Workshops and Clinics:</strong> We regularly host workshops and clinics on various topics, such as bike maintenance, riding techniques, and safety tips. These sessions are designed to enhance your cycling knowledge and skills.</li>
</ul>

<center><h2>Community Involvement</h2></center>
<center><img src="~/images/logo/company involvement.jpeg" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" /></center>
<p>At Zoro Cycle Shop, we believe in giving back to the community that has supported us over the years. We are involved in several community initiatives and events:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Charity Rides:</strong> We organize and participate in charity bike rides to raise funds for local causes. These events are a great way to promote cycling and support our community.</li>
    <li><strong>Local Sponsorships:</strong> We sponsor local cycling clubs, teams, and events. Our goal is to promote cycling as a healthy and sustainable mode of transportation and recreation.</li>
    <li><strong>Educational Programs:</strong> We collaborate with schools and community organizations to offer educational programs on cycling safety and maintenance. Our aim is to encourage more people to take up cycling and do so safely.</li>
</ul>

<center><h2>Customer Testimonials</h2></center>
<center><img src="~/images/logo/testomonical.jpeg" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" /></center>
<p>We are proud of the positive feedback we receive from our customers. Here are some testimonials from satisfied customers:</p>
<blockquote>
    <p>"Zoro Cycle Shop has been my go-to bike shop for years. The staff is incredibly knowledgeable and always willing to help. Whether I need a new bike or a quick repair, they never disappoint." - Jane Smith</p>
</blockquote>
