</blockquote>

<center><h2>Our Future Goals</h2></center>
<center><img src="~/images/logo/future goal.jpeg" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" /></center>
<p>As we look to the future, we have several goals to continue improving and expanding our services:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Expand Our Product Range:</strong> We plan to introduce new products and brands to offer our customers even more choices. Our goal is to stay at the forefront of cycling trends and technology.</li>
    <li><strong>Enhance Customer Experience:</strong> We are constantly looking for ways to improve the shopping experience, both in-store and online. This includes upgrading our website, expanding our online store, and offering more personalized services.</li>
    <li><strong>Promote Sustainable Practices:</strong> We are committed to promoting environmentally sustainable practices. This includes offering eco-friendly products and encouraging cycling as a green mode of transportation.</li>
    <li><strong>Increase Community Engagement:</strong> We aim to strengthen our ties with the community through more events, sponsorships, and educational programs. Our goal is to promote cycling and contribute to the well-being of our community.</li>
</ul>

<center><h2>Contact Us</h2></center>
<center><img src="~/images/logo/contact us.png" height="100px" style="border-radius:50px" /></center>
<p>If you have any questions or would like to learn more about Zoro Cycle Shop, please do not hesitate to contact us. You can visit us at our store, call us, or reach out via email. We are here to help you with all your cycling needs.</p>
<p>Thank you for choosing Zoro Cycle Shop. We look forward to serving you and helping you enjoy your cycling journey. Happy cycling!</p>
